\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Software development skills: these skills (version control, programming
 style, software design, debugging, testing, VVUQ) are language-independent
 and apply to any software development effort.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Languages: different languages (Python, C++, R, MATLAB, etc.)
