\begin_layout Subsection
Services Provided
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
THWUC will provide the following services:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
`Learning Lunches': regular (monthly, bimonthly, or weekly depending on
 demand) brown bag lunches where students can learn a new computational
 skill during lunch hour.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Workshops: quarterly (or so) classes dedicated to more intensive training.
 These workshop will be similar to the recent Software Carpentry boot camp
 (which was oversubscribed by 150 students).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Help/Forum: if there is demand, we can create some kind of support forum
 to help students solve computational questions and acquire further training.
\end_layout

